   END.
   FIND FIRST LEVERANTOR WHERE LEVERANTOR.LEVNAMN = lev2 NO-LOCK NO-ERROR.
   IF AVAILABLE LEVERANTOR THEN DO:
      kod2 = LEVERANTOR.LEVKOD.      
   END.
   RUN KONSKOLL5.P (INPUT kod1, INPUT kod2, OUTPUT TABLE kons_mtrl).
